These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, doctor, fisherman, project-manager
1. the project-manager is on the left or right of the journalist##3
2. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5
3. the doctor is not to the left of the fisherman##8
4. the doctor is on the left of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | fisherman | doctor | project-manager | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, tea, juice
1. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | water | tea | cola | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, pomegranate, apple, onion
1. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating onion##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person eating onion##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | kiwi | onion | pomegranate | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, magic-tricks, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | card-games | magic-tricks | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-5::.
