3. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |       3       |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | surfing | volleyball | basketball |

