.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, zucchini, radish, pomegranate
1. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating orange is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
4. the person eating orange is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | pomegranate | zucchini | orange | radish |

